{
  "stem": "17372.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to play that tune while he was parading.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then they started to one day make segregation of children, start to take all children from parents, from mothers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That cry is unimaginable, how they put the children-- these mothers crying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this is-- on that occasion, my nephew, which was a very young boy-- my two nephews, they run into toilet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They call latrine-- it's a big room with board with holes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they jump into the exhumes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they saved their lives through this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they took away [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] those children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And sadistically, they played through the speakers-- loudspeakers, they played the tune, '[SPEAKING GERMAN],' 'Mommy, Buy Me a Little Horsey.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Background-- they played that tune.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yes, this is unforgettable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the Russian were coming closer-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't mention before that Oskar Schindler had the factory Emalia Enamel Works on the outskirt of Cracow but not in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there was working 700 people going under guard every day to work and coming back at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But after short time, he used his influence, his bribing, he fix that he was allowed to build barracks in his factory.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So the people didn't have to come back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was already like win-- [? tattersall. ?] And no German was-- soldier was allowed to go into factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he had 700 people working there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when the Russian were coming closer, he got order to liquidate the factory and to send us-- send the people to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Instead, he went to Brunnlitz, Brnenec-- this is in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He, he bought old, unused knitting factory-- it was before.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
